The paper deals with the problem of generating coherent and succinct stories for long videos, which involves bridging vision and natural language. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the proposed methods involve the use of recurrent neural networks and reinforcement learning, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
